Fallbrook Vintage Car Show

The Fallbrook Vintage Car Club restarts its annual vintage car show.  This after COVID forced its cancellation in 2020.  And they have a new venue!  So the show will now be held at the Potter Junior High School in Fallbrook, California.

And there will be over 350 cars, more than 60 vendors, food and entertainment.  Plus, unique to this show is the passion and dedication shown by its members through the official poster they create and sell.  Because the custom poster both promotes and commemorates the show and what’s special about it each year.  And that’s just cool!

Fallbrook Vintage Car Show

Date: Sunday, May 30th, 2021
Location: Potter Junior High School – Fallbrook, California
Admission: Free
Parking: Free
Show start: 9 AM – Colors Presentation & National Anthem
Awards: 3 PM
Show end: 4 PM

*Please note: iDriveSoCal does not host this event.  So if you’d like to learn more about the event please contact the Fallbrook Vintage Car Club.   And that includes more specific details about attending, displaying your vehicle, and becoming a vendor or sponsor.
